RIDU, the <i><b> Journal of Educational Innovation Universitaria </i></b>, is a publication for the university community, which seeks to highlight those experiences of innovation and improvement in teaching at the university level. The experiences of teaching innovation originating within specific subjects, are often adaptable to other disciplines that may seem distant. For this reason, the journal published work teaching innovation respecting any academic discipline. <br> This journal is indexed in:<a href="http://www.doaj.org/doaj?func=search&template=&uiLanguage=en&query=revista+%60%27innovaci%C3%B3+docent+universit%C3%A0ria&filter=media%3A%22journal%22"><b>DOAJ.</b>
